review: Dr Harini is an excellent periodontist.  She  carefully listened  to everything I told her. Her diagnosis  done after a thorough examination was absolutely spot on. The treatment worked perfectly.  The follow up was prompt as well. She  only suggests those tests treatments and procedures which are absolutely necessary. It is heartening to see a doctor who is not only  extremely professional and skilled but also has a lot of empathy and concern for their patients.
reply_text: Thank you for your valuable feedback!

review: The service I received from Dr. Harini is excellent. She is informative, patient and compassionate. I had laser surgery done it has healed pretty well, I also had burning sensation in my gums which has healed with her help as well. Over all experience was great. Highly recommended
reply_text: Thank you for your valuable feedback

review: I have been suffering from mouth sores and soft gums since some time. I went to clips and implants clinic for consultation during 2021 and Dr. Harini Reddy Garu performed laser flap surgery and I was completely relieved of the discomfort, soreness and I am grateful to the kind doctor for the treatment. Not only the treatment, her guidance  on how to manage gum health and hygiene and the proper way to massage gums was excellent. I am grateful to her and  I follow the guidelines  and feel happy and comfortable and I wish had I consulted Dr. Harini Garu earliest to my visit I would have kept my oral condition better. I am grateful to Dr. Harini Reddy for the treatment and guidance and may God bless her with health, wealth, success and many more laurels.
reply_text: Thank you so much for your valuable feedback

review: I had bleeding gums & was indeed scared; right at the time I had landed to Dr Harini via Practo - who made sure to make me feel calm & comfortable at first, later briefing the real cause behind it, in process I had to redirect few of my conventional ways & I’m glad that I did. Again no unnecessary demand or extra seatings - if it’s working well - you’re good to go :) Thank you for the best experience.
reply_text: Thank you for your valuable feedback
